            "title": "盤中速報 - 竑騰(7751)股價拉至漲停，漲停價2645.0元，成交481張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>竑騰(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7751:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7751\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7751-TW</a>)27日11:38上漲240元，股價漲停報2645.0元，委買2,000張、委賣36,000張，成交481張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為半導體自動化生產及光學檢測設備。治具、零件及維修收入。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>竑騰(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7751:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7751\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7751-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲26.91%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.47%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+539 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+2 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+521 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+16 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
